36:45.871 --> 36:47.998
And for us to be us again.

36:57.132 --> 36:58.759
Of course I forgive you.

36:58.842 --> 37:00.385
And I'm sorry, too.

37:00.469 --> 37:02.012
Lo siento.

37:02.095 --> 37:03.889
Lo siento, lo siento,
lo siento.

